default&#xa0; 
defaultIn respect of 
defaulta
defaultnti–icing and 
defaultd
defaulte-icing Gatwick has increased its liquid storage capacity from 170,000 litres to over 500,000 litres and additionally holds 45,000kg of solid media 
default(i.e. salt) 
defaultwhich is sufficient for a ‘normal’ season or ten days of extreme conditions.  There is also a co
defaultntingency temporary storage facility for a further 147,000 litres.  Gatwick has also increased its de-icing fleet from three to six. 
