defaultThe welfare of the passenger 
defaultis paramount to Gatwick and our Snow Plan includes provisions for 
defaultsleeping areas with beds, blankets
default, 
defaultfood and water.
default We have in stock 4,000 blankets, 600 mattresses, four pallets of water (8,000 bottles of water), 600 folding beds, 20 snow shovels, four baby bottle warmers, 10 travel cots and a mixture of baby food and nappies.
